# Jenkins CI/CD Guide

## Pipeline Setup
```groovy
pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm install'
                sh 'npm run build'
            }
        }
        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm test'
            }
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm run deploy'
            }
        }
    }
}
```

## Key Features
- Automated builds
- Plugin ecosystem
- Distributed builds
- Pipeline as code
